text: <@U2H61EJSG|summer> uploaded a file: <https://uncorked.slack.com/files/summer/F3M183SSE/app-debug.apk|app-debug.apk> and commented: <@U13GPDA1F> Here is the newest version of Gauge. I changed the UI a little bit to accommodate more buttons, added some additional information for photo/video stats, updated how we are gathering phone call stats so that it actually works as expected, and fixed a few other small bugs. I spent quite a bit of time trying to figure out how to work with Google Hangouts as the default SMS app, but I haven’t found anything promising yet. I will keep you posted!
